{"tid":1648904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國學者王萬里指港法院無權覆核《緊急法》","createTime":"2019-10-12T12:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T12:57:11.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a87f7dd192ab1c14ae38f24a51a7033c141e45ae","tid":1648904,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:01:49.000Z","msg":"內地學者指港法院無權覆核《緊急法》<br />\n<br />\n王萬里今(12日)撰文指，《緊急法》為回歸前的原有法律，全國人大常委會已在1997年審查當時的香港法律是否符合《基本法》，經適應化後採用為香港特別行政區的法律，所以法院無權就《緊急法》是否違憲作審查，不能以司法覆核方式質疑及推翻經全國人大常委會確認的合憲性，否則是對全國人大常委會憲制權力及權威的挑戰及侵奪。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191012/mobile/bkn-20191012181901999-1012_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191012%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191012181901999-1012_00822_001.html&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=9605e4fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191012/mobile/bkn-20191012181901999-1012_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"802e790d57691a3920d46340e3cc75fb48e88c63","tid":1648904,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:02:39.000Z","msg":"一句野解釋晒點解場運動會輸<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/emwPhS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/emwPhS</a>"},{"pid":"141ed327aae5ae02f58cbed08d36cd2bee18c384","tid":1648904,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:04:11.000Z","msg":"覺得活動好亂既人入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"695d514efe79d1723b32757613844375f3a68a59","tid":1648904,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:04:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <ins> <div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 公民抗爭式交稅<br />\n<br />\n香港人真 &middot; 反抗！！！<br />\n<br />\n入黎跟住做啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n＞【<a href=\"https://lih.kg/16